highlights.text: “El Fin del Mundo” by La La Love You and Axolotes Mexicanos has been on Top Songs Spain the longest, at 1305 days straight.
“Big Poe (feat. Sk8brd)” by Tyler, The Creator and Pharrell Williams is the highest new entry on Top Songs Spain at #170.
Beéle has the most spots on Top Songs Spain. “La Plena - W Sound 05” is the highest at #1.
“El Efecto” by Rauw Alejandro and Chencho Corleone is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Spain, up 58 spots at #129.
